{
  "stem": "10.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to escape.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, would you join me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't tell him yes or no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was thinking about it, if to join him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came to the decision not to, because I told myself, when I escape, and I probably would be able-- I would be lucky enough to escape because of my languages.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I speak German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he is a German, speaks only German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I thought myself, OK, I will be lucky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I get out, I'm in hiding somewhere, and I can maybe survive the war to the end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we knew already what's going on the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans had to retreat since Stalingrad, and the western front wasn't too rosy either.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were beaten, and the Russians came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everywhere they came to a camp in Poland, they burnt or destroyed the camp, killed all the people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I thought to myself, no, I'm not escaping.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can myself save myself, but what about all the other ones I could help who suffer-- when they suffer?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stay in the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to him, no, I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I helped him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I gave him my watch, because I was allowed to carry a watch because I was a doctor, you see.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I gave him my watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day-- and it's Sunday-- I was in the camp, because every night I was free.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could go to the main camp, you see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They allowed me to go because of my arm band.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans see I'm a functionary, so I could go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, naturally, where do I go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To the hospital, and I talk to my friends, to the doctors, to the nurses I know.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
